        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued November 11 at 12:41AM EST by NWS Pittsburgh PA</headline>
        <description>A band of snow showers could result in periods of low visibility
and hazardous road conditions for the next 3 to 4 hours across
Clarion and Jefferson counties. Untreated roads could be icy
during the early morning commute.
